N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 163.1 - Application

State Regulations

Any person, firm, partnership, corporation, association or
exchange lawfully operating in the State of New York, marketing New York State
farm products, either fresh or processed, and desiring to use an official New

York State brand or trademark upon said products shall make application for
such use upon a form provided by the department. Notes
